ers-say-company-not-adding-staff-for-early-opening-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkers%20told%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20was%20making%20some%20adjustments%20in%20terms%20of%20daily%20scheduling%20and%20operations.%20They%20also%20said%20it%20wasn't%20investing%20in%20additional%20staff%20hours%20to%20handle%20the%20extra%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20raised%20some%20red%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20an%20absolute%20nightmare%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20front-end%20manager%20told%20me%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20checkout%20lanes%20at%20a%20Costco%20warehouse%20in%20Wisconsin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68893ffaf748d8c055f67ff3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20checkout%20lanes%20weren't%20immediately%20open%20at%209%20a.m.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20weeks%20have%20gone%20by%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20new%20hours%20are%20working%20reasonably%20well%20%E2%80%94%20for%20executive%20members%20and%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20retail%20analyst%20Michael%20Lasser%20said%20in%20a%20note%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20the%20move%20could%20give%20Costco%20a%20financial%20lift%20this%20quarter%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Costco%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20colleague%20Talia%20Lakritz%20and%20I%20each%20upgraded%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-ways-shop-without-membership-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGold%20Star%20memberships%3C%2Fa%3E%20specifically%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20both%20visited%20Costco%20several%20times%20this%20month%20during%20the%20new%20executive%20hours%20(she's%20in%20New%20