20because%20I've%20never%20developed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkid-diagnosed-with-life-threatening-allergy-how-what-we-did-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekey%20symptoms%20of%20anaphylaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20when%20your%20throat%20closes%20up%2C%20you%20can't%20breathe%2C%20and%20you%20get%20circulation%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Kitt%20Medical%2C%20I%20was%20terrified%20of%20using%20a%20pen.%20Until%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20my%20mom%20carried%20them%20for%20me.%20When%20I%20went%20to%20university%2C%20I%20was%20going%20out%20alone%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20carry%20this%20bulky%20pen%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20final%20year%20at%20university%2C%20studying%20product%20design%2C%20we%20were%20told%20to%20develop%20something%20we%20cared%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERedesigning%20the%20pen%20without%20engineering%20skills%20wasn't%20possible.%20I%20started%20brainstorming%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can't%20redesign%20the%20pen%2C%20what%20can%20I%20do%20that%20builds%20around%20the%20existing%20one%20and%20plugs%20the%20gaps%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gaps%20were%20that%20adrenaline%20pens%20typically%20expire%20within%2012%20to%2018%20months%2C%20they%20are%20inconvenient%20to%20carry%2C%20and%20most%20people%20aren't%20aware%20of%20them%20or%20trained%20to%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20idea%2C%20stemming%20from%20fire%20extinguishers%20and%20defibrillators%2C%20was%20a%20wall-mounted%20kit%20with%20a%20screen%20and%20speakers.%20Through%20pilots%20and%20testing%2C%20we%20whittled%20it%20down%20to%20a%20glorified%20briefcase%20that%20can%20hold%20pens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220966f910-ec83-4d95-86ef-288d3c7ae874%5C%22%3EBuilding%20with%20no%20background%20in%20medicine%20or%20business%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20new%20standard%20for%20allergy%20care%20%E2%80%94%20a%20kit%20like%20a%20defibrillator%20in%20every%20school%2C%20workplace%2C%20restaurant%2C%20or%20stadium.%20If%20someone%20has%20a%20reaction%2C%20a%20trained%20staff%20member%20runs%20to%20the%20kit%2C%20takes%20it%20to%20that%20person%2C%20gets%20the%20adrenaline%20pen%2C%20follows%20the%20training%2C%20and%20saves%20their%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224489%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zak%20Marks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6889fd0c3d5881a51c1e3c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZak%20Marks%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20Kitt%20Medical%20while%20at%20university.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kitt%20Medical%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20a%20reality%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20background%20in%20medicine.%20I%20had%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduated-from-stanford-cant-land-job-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egraduated%20from%20university%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20run%20my%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20and%20brother-in-law%20advised%20me%20that%20I%20needed%20a%20cofounder.%20I%20was%20luckily%20introduced%20to%20James%20Cohen%2C%20who%20was%20in%20sales%2C%20worked%20in%20schools%2C%20and%20had%20an%20operational%20and%20finance%20head%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20and%20I%20worked%20together%20to%20raise%20about%20%C2%A3100%2C000%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20in%202021.%20I%20quit%20freelancing%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20furlough%20job%2C%20and%20we%20went%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20invested%20in%20marketing%2C%20conferences%2C%20prototype%20creation%2C%20manufacturing%20resources%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20built%20a%20website%20to%20monitor%20the%20kits%20and%20support%20pharmaceutical%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f34ce13f-5f01-43dc-a61e-b4d02fd1b0f5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesigning%20the%20product%20from%20scratch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kit%20itself%20isn't%20a%20medical%20product%2C%20so%20there%20wasn't%20red%20tape%20around%20that.%20But%20we%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20provide%20an%20all-in-one%20service%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20get%20a%20special%20license%20to%20distribute%20medicine%20to%20sell%20the%20kits%20with%20adrenaline%20pens%20in%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20hire%20a%20regulatory%20affairs%20consultant%20to%20hold%20that%20license%20and%20were%20put%20on%20a%20waitlist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20worked%20with%20consultants%20and%20doctors%20in%20the%20field%20who%20love%20what%20we're%20doing%20and%20want%20to%20help%20us.%20One%20of%20the%20best%20pieces%20of%20advice%20I've%20ever%20received%20was%20to%20hire%20people%20smarter%20than%20you%20to%20do%20the%20things%20you%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20piloted%20the%20kit%20in%20schools.%20In%20November%202022%2C%20we%20raised%20more%20capital%2C%20largely%20through%20grants%20and%20pitching%20competitions%2C%20as%20we%20were%20keen%20to%20hold%20a%20majority%20share%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kitt%20Medical%20kit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6889fd6ef748d8c055f6843f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222730%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Kitt%20Medical%20is%20marketed%20as%20being%20like%20a%20defibrillator%20for%20allergies.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kitt%20Medical%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20those%20schools%20and%20replaced%20their%20old%20kits%20with%20our%20new%20ones.%20By%20then%2C%20we%20had%20functioning%20software%20and%20a%20license%20to%20sell%20medication.%20%3Cspan%3EEach%20year%20we%20will%20send%20out%20new%20adrenaline%20pens%20to%20replace%20expired%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20having%20the%20license%2C%20we%20weren't%20taking%20any%20payment%20for%20medication%3B%20the%20pilot%20schools%20were%20getting%20their%20medication%20separately.%20%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20waiting%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20waitlist%20building%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20keep%20the%20momentum%20up%20with%20constant%20marketing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20we%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20sell%20to%20businesses%2C%20having%20already%20been%20supplying%20schools%20for%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20can%20be%20prohibitive%20because%20adrenaline%20is%20a%20prescription-only%20medicine.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20UK%20business%20with%20an%20occupational%20health%20plan%2C%20you%20can%20purchase%20spare%20adrenaline%20pens.%20That%20opened%20a%20lot%20of%20doors%20to%20sell%20to%20qualifying%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zak%20Marks%2C%20left%2C%20and%20James%20Cohen%2C%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6889fdd385e81483682eea97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZak%20Marks%2C%20left%2C%20and%20cofounder%20James%20Cohen%2C%20right%2C%20run%20Kitt%20Medical%20together.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kitt%20Medical%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20revenue%20is%20good%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-founders-explain-grow-your-company-referrals-2023-10%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522First%252C%2520it%2520was%2520seeing%2520what%2Cdouble%2520her%2520revenue%252C%2520she%2520said.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowing%20organically%20through%20referrals%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20our%20path%20to%20scaling%20right%20now%20is%20to%20keep%20launching%20kits%20in%20different%20sectors.%20But%20our%20biggest%20success%20is%20the%20lives%20we've%20potentially%20saved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20Kitts%20have%20been%20used%20to%20treat%2017%20life-threatening%20allergic%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20set%20out%20to%20be%20an%20entrepreneur.%20I%20didn't%20think%20I%20had%20it%20in%20me.%20Sometimes%2C%20