nce%20cameras%20and%20who%20have%20the%20power%20to%20control%20elevator%20systems%20and%20turnstiles%20and%20alert%20police%20if%20there%20is%20an%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20buildings%20have%20these%20rooms%2C%20but%20more%20landlords%20are%20considering%20them%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmick%20suggested%20the%20attack%20could%20also%20accelerate%20the%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20building%20operations.%20AI%20can%20be%20coupled%20with%20closed-circuit%20surveillance%20systems%20to%20recognize%20weapons%20instantly%20or%20even%20threatening%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20agree%20that%20this%20is%20an%20isolated%20act%20of%20violence%2C%20but%20there%20still%20is%20the%20sense%20now%20that%20this%20is%20something%20we%20have%20to%20prepare%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmick%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20saying%20we%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20details%20here%2C%20and%20what%20else%20can%20we%20do%20to%20help%20mitigate%20this%20from%20happening%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f3cca6f-cf20-483c-bf18-d0af43162234%5C%22%3EAn%20industry%20in%20mourning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20mass%20shootings%20have%20become%20familiar%20to%20the%20public%20in%20recent%20decades%2C%20Monday's%20attack%20brought%20the%20terrifying%20scene%20to%20some%20of%20the%20nation's%20top%20companies%2C%20notably%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvern-perry-blackstone-strategic-partners-career-advice-secondaries-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlackstone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%241.2%20trillion%20asset%20manager%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Football%20League%2C%20which%20NYC%20mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20said%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanhattan-office-shooter-shane-tamura-left-study-my-brain-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20target%20of%20the%20gunman%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20at%20around%206%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20the%20lone%20gunman%20walked%20into%20the%20lobby%20of%20345%20Park%20Avenue%20with%20a%20semiautomatic%20rifle%20and%20opened%20fire%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Police%20Department.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20real%20estate%20executives%2C%20the%20shooter%20also%20killed%20an%20NYPD%20officer%20hired%20to%20protect%20the%20property%20and%20a%20security%20guard.%20The%20gunman%20died%20of%20a%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20estate%20executives%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20described%20Monday's%20tragedy%20as%20the%20industry's%20biggest%20blow%20in%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20since%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%20that%20brought%20down%20the%20Twin%20Towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMary%20Ann%20Tighe%2C%20the%20New%20York%20CEO%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20services%20firm%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20get%20through%20the%20day%20with%20our%20hearts%20so%20heavy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrazy%20bad%20things%20shouldn't%20happen%20to%20anyone%2C%20but%20it%20stuns%20when%20you%20know%20people%20involved%20and%20you%20also%20know%20how%20special%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20think%20I'm%20just%20kind%20of%20dealing%20with%20the%20tragedy%20and%20not%20thinking%20about%20how%20does%20this%20relate%20to%20that%2C%20or%20this%20or%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Mechanic%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20law%20firm%20Fried%20Frank's%20real%20estate%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sure%20that%20there%20are%20conversations%20that%20are%20going%20on%2C%20and%20we'll%20see%20what%20people%20decide%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Mechanic%20said%20of%20security%20questions%20swirling%20through%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Real%20Estate%20Board%20of%20New%20York%2C%20the%20industry's%20main%20lobbying%20group%20and%20professional%20association%2C%20whose%20office%20is%20just%20across%20the%20street%20from%2