%20days%20past%20due%20when%20the%20data%20was%20collected%20in%20May%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20was%20a%20warning%20sign%20for%20for-profit%20schools%3A%20It%20found%20that%2030%25%20of%20borrowers%20who%20attended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-for-profit-education-student-debt-quick-degrees-fraud-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor-profit%20institutions%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20behind%20on%20their%20payments%2C%20compared%20to%2016%25%20of%20borrowers%20at%20public%20schools%20and%2014%25%20of%20borrowers%20at%20private%20schools.%20If%20nonpayment%20rates%20do%20not%20improve%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eby%20next%20year%2C%20schools%20on%20that%20list%20risk%20losing%20federal%20student%20aid%2C%20including%20student%20loans%20and%20Pell%20Grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosmetology%20and%20barber%20schools%20were%20high%20on%20the%20nonpayment%20list%3A%20Networks%20Barber%20College%20in%20Illinois%20and%20Washington%20Barber%20College%20in%20Arkansas%20had%2067%25%20nonpayment%20rates%2C%20and%20Foster's%20Cosmetology%20and%20Barber%20College%20in%20Mississippi%20had%20a%2064%25%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20for-profit%20colleges%3A%20Independence%20Community%20College%2C%20a%20public%20Kansas%20school%2C%20has%20a%2049%25%20nonpayment%20rate%2C%20and%20Carolina%20Christian%20College%2C%20a%20private%20North%20Carolina%20school%2C%20has%20a%2061%25%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20college%20or%20student%20debt%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20the%20department%20has%20not%20been%20collecting%20data%20on%20the%20number%20of%20graduates%20who%20are%20in%20delinquency%20or%20default%20on%20their%20student%20loans%20because%20of%20an%20ongoing%20pandemic%20pause%20on%20collections.%20It%20also%20meant%20that%20the%20department%20was%20not%20penalizing%20colleges%20for%20high%20default%20rates%20by%20cutting%20off%20their%20access%20to%20federal%20student%20aid%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20was%20in%20place%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trump's%20administration%20restarted%20collections%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-react-default-collections-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefaulted%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20tracking%20is%20back%20on.%20Colleges%20could%20lose%20aid%20if%20they%20exceed%2030%25%20of%20the%20cohort%20default%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20the%20percentage%20of%20borrowers%20who%20default%20on%20their%20debt%20%E2%80%94%20for%20three%20consecutive%20years%2C%20or%2040%25%20for%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreston%20Cooper%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20conservative%20think%20tank%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20said%20that%20with%20collections%20having%20resumed%20on%20defaulted%20student%20loans%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20rate%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cohort%20default%20rate%20has%20been%20essentially%20a%20non-factor%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20it's%20entirely%20possible%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20come%20back%20with%20a%20vengeance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooper%20said%20it%20could%20take%20at%20least%20a%20year%20for%20schools%20on%20the%20list%20to%20actually%20lose%20federal%20student%20aid%20because%20it%20takes%20time%20for%20defaults%20to%20reflect%20in%20the%20data%20the%20department%20collects%2C%20and%20schools%20can%20also%20attempt%20to%20appeal.%20However%2C%20that%20time%20can%20go%20by%20quickly%2C%20and%20he%20said%20that%20it's%20in%20schools'%20best%20interests%20to%20start%20helping%20borrowers%20with%20repayment%20before%20it's%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSchools%20do%20have%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20runway%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20they%20cannot%20plead%20ignorance.%20They%20have%20plenty%20of%20lead%20time%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20avoid%20the%20worst%20consequences%20of%20triggering%20the%20cohort%20default%20rates.%20And%20if%20they%20don't%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that's%20on%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c95745d9-93b0-4ebb-a7d5-d4897b5dc1a5%5C%22%3EAn%20incoming%20default%20wave%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20latest%20nonpayment%20data%20was%20released%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20in%20May%20urged%20all%20colleges%20that%20receive%20federal%20aid%20to%20remind%20students%20of%20their%20options%20to%20repay%20their%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20too%20long%2C%20insufficient%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20structures%20have%20allowed%20U.S.%20universities%20to%20saddle%20students%20with%20enormous%20debt%20loads%20without%20paying%20enough%20attention%20to%20whether%20their%20own%20graduates%20are%20truly%20prepared%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20labor%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Linda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20education%20secretary%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2Fus-department-of-education-reminds-colleges-and-universities-of-their-obligations-help-struggling-borrowers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolyn%20Fast%2C%20director%20of%20higher%20education%20policy%20at%20the%20progressive%20think%20tank%20The%20Century%20Foundation%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20enforcing%20accountability%20will%20be%20difficult.%20The%20Department%20of%20Education%20estimated%20that%2010%20million%20borrowers%20could%20default%20this%20summer%20after%20the%20collections%20restart%2C%20and%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-dismantling-department-education-means-supreme-court-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edismantle%20the%20department%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fire%20staff%20mean%20that%20borrowers%20will%20have%20limited%20resources%20to%20get%20help%20determining%20their%20repayment%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutting%20the%20department%20also%20means%20that%20oversight%20over%20for-profit%20schools%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20shut%20down%20or%20faced%20litigation%20over%20the%20past%20years%20over%20accusations%20of%20predatory%20behavior%20that%20loaded%20students%20up%20with%20unaffordable%20debt%2C%20will%20be%20minimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20programs%20out%20there%20that%20are%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20federal%20money%2C%20that%20are%20just%20not%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20for%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Fast%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nonpayment%20data%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20every%20school%20on%20the%20list%20will%20lose%20federal%20aid.%20Fast%20said%20that%20schools%20will%20likely%20bolster%20outreach%20to%20students%20to%20mitigate%20the%20problem%20by%20reestablishing%20contact%20with%20graduates%20and%20informing%20them%20of%20existing%20repayment%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20latest%20spending%20law%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminated%20existing%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20replaced%20them%20with%20two%2C%20less%20generous%20options%20that%20will%20go%20into%20effect%20in%20July%202026.%20This%20means%20that%20borrowers%20will%20have%20to%20navigate%20a%20changing%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erepayment%20system%20while%20working%20to%20avoid%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20flag%20that%20these%20are%20institutions%20who%20have%20very%2C%20very%20high%20rates%20of%20student%20loan%20delinq