%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDogpound%2C%20a%20boutique%20Manhattan%20gym%20where%20Karlie%20Kloss%2C%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20and%20Hugh%20Jackman%20have%20been%20known%20to%20work%20out%2C%20is%20already%20exclusive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-out-hugh-jackman-ashley-graham-gym-dogpound-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDogpound%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20planned%20to%20move%20to%20a%20referral-only%20model%2C%20says%20Xander%20Hodge%2C%20the%20gym's%20general%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Dogpound%20discontinued%20the%20most%20affordable%20%E2%80%94%20%24708-a-month%20%E2%80%94%20membership%2C%20which%20covered%20just%20four%20personal%20training%20sessions%20a%20month.%20And%20they%20added%20a%20top%20membership%20tier%20that%20allows%20for%20unlimited%20sessions%20and%20costs%20%24100%2C000%20a%20year.%20The%20idea%2C%20says%20Hodge%2C%20is%20to%20preserve%20the%20feel%20of%20a%20committed%2C%20tight-knit%20community%20while%20ensuring%20the%20privacy%20of%20their%20A-list%20clientele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20afternoon%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20try%20a%20group%20class.%20The%20all-black%20space%20was%20smaller%20than%20your%20standard%20commercial%20gym%2C%20sleek%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20frills%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20showers%2C%20though%20Hodge%20tells%20me%20they%20hope%20to%20add%20some%20as%20part%20of%20a%20planned%20expansion.%20After%20two%20sessions%20with%20the%20same%20trainer%2C%20clients%20are%20required%20to%20rotate%20to%20someone%20new%2C%20part%20of%20the%20gym's%20strategy%20to%20make%20sure%20everyone%20gets%20to%20know%20one%20another%20on%20a%20first-name%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20just%20three%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mom%20of%20three%20who%20said%20she%20has%20worked%20out%20at%20Dogpound%20two%20times%20a%20week%20since%202020%2C%20and%20her%20friend%2C%20who%20occasionally%20tags%20along%20for%20a%20class.%20(%26quot%3BShe%20is%20our%20reigning%20member%2C%26quot%3B%20Hodge%20says%20of%20the%20mom%20after%20the%20class%20ended.%20%26quot%3BAnytime%20we%20have%20a%20charity%20event%2C%20she%20is%20the%20first%20one%20there%20bringing%20three%20friends!%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workout%20was%20tough%2C%20a%20mix%20of%20dumbbell%20and%20bodyweight%20exercises%20and%20cardio.%20With%20so%20few%20of%20us%2C%20the%20individualized%20instruction%20was%20great.%20The%20class%20was%20also%20fun.%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20open%20my%20classmates%20were%20to%20socializing%20in%20between%20sets%2C%20chatting%20about%20weekend%20plans%20and%20bad%20dates.%20Two%20personal%20training%20sessions%20were%20happening%20nearby%2C%20and%20every%20instructor%20who%20passed%20our%20class%20introduced%20themselves%20with%20a%20friendly%20fist%20bump.%20One%20did%20a%20handstand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20felt%20remarkably%20warm%20and%20welcoming.%20Unlike%20the%20oversubscribed%20gyms%20and%20full-to-capacity%20SoulCycle%20classes%20I%20was%20used%20to%2C%20here%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20working%20out%20among%20old%20friends.%20It%20was%20intimate%20and%2C%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3Eluxurious%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20I%20left%2C%20I%20caught%20myself%20running%20the%20math%20to%20see%20if%20I%20could%20swing%20becoming%20a%20regular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20night%2C%20I%20joined%20Dogpound's%20Tuesday%20night%20run%20club%20on%20a%20running%20path%20along%20New%20York's%20Hudson%20River.%20The%20club%20is%20free%20and%20open%20to%20the%20public%2C%20but%20the%20seven%20other%20people%20who%20showed%20up%20were%20all%20current%20or%20former%20Dogpound%20members%20or%20staff.%20As%20we%20made%20our%20way%20past%20Battery%20Park%2C%20with%20a%20view%20out%20to%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%2C%20half%20the%20group%20kept%20up%20a%20competitive%20pace%20%E2%80%94%20one%20was%20a%20serial%20ultramarathoner%20%E2%80%94%20while%20I%20hung%20back%20with%20the%20more%20talkative%20runners%2C%20keeping%20a%20more%20leisurely%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228434%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dogpound%20front%20door%20in%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a4cca85e81483682ef4fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225623%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20struck%20up%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20fellow%20first-timer.%20She%20had%20joined%20Dogpound%20as%20a%2030th%20birthday%20gift%20to%20herself%20and%20strength%20trains%20at%20the%20gym%20twice%20a%20week.%20Her%20enthusiasm%20echoed%20the%20feeling%20I'd%20had%20the%20night%20before%3A%20With%20fewer%20people%20around%2C%20it's%20easier%20to%20meet%20and%20bond%20with%20like-minded%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20very%20different%20experience%20from%20Equinox%2C%20her%20previous%20gym.%20There%2C%20she%20says%2C%20she%20and%20her%20sister%20had%20split%20a%20single%20%24325%20membership%20card%2C%20passing%20it%20back%20and%20forth%20for%20months.%20The%20front%20desk%2C%20she%20said%2C%20never%20realized%20they%20weren't%20the%20same%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Feve-upton-clark%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EEve%20Upton-Clark%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20features%20writer%20covering%20culture%20and%20society.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-yorks-hottest-club-the-invite-only-gym-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753948981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a4d08f748d8c055f68ea0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-yorks-hottest-club-the-invite-only-gym-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20a%20great%20work