Cli%3EThe%20exemption%20triggered%20a%2020%25%20drop%20in%20copper%20futures%20on%20the%20COMEX%20exchange.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETraders%20now%20face%20excess%20inventory%2C%20with%20COMEX%20stockpiles%20at%20a%2021-year%20high.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECopper%20traders%20were%20caught%20off%20guard%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20refined%20copper%20was%20excluded%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20new%20tariffs%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20large%20stockpiles%20and%20rapidly%20falling%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20copper%20futures%20on%20New%20York's%20COMEX%20exchange%20plunged%2020%25%20in%20one%20day%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20intraday%20drop%20since%20the%20contract%20began%20trading%20in%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sell-off%20followed%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20decision%20to%20exempt%20refined%20copper%20from%20a%20sweeping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcopper-prices-trump-tariffs-commodities-trade-war-fcx-scco-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E50%25%20import%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20takes%20effect%20August%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20tariff%20will%20only%20apply%20to%20copper%20products%20like%20pipes%2C%20wires%2C%20and%20sheets%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20refined%20copper%2C%20the%20most%20widely%20imported%20form%20of%20the%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20stunned%20traders%20who%20had%20spent%20months%20shipping%20refined%20copper%20into%20the%20US%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20tariff.%20Copper%20is%20a%20major%20industrial%20metal%20used%20in%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20applications%20and%20sectors%2C%20including%20construction%20and%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20first%20suggested%20copper%20duties%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20COMEX%20prices%20surged%20and%20traders%20rushed%20to%20import%20the%20metal%20before%20tariffs%20set%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrices%20have%20been%20rising%20this%20year%20largely%20because%20the%20market%20has%20been%20front-running%20the%20tariff%20policy%20and%20not%20because%20the%20demand%20picture%20has%20been%20improving%20or%20because%20the%20supply%20has%20actually%20been%20tightening%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Ewa%20Manthey%2C%20a%20commodities%20strategist%20at%20ING.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECopper%20futures%20had%20been%20trading%20at%20a%2028%25%20premium%20on%20the%20US%20exchange%20compared%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fcopper-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELondon%20Metal%20Exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20spread%20that%20crashed%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20traders%20face%20a%20potentially%20massive%20inventory%20overhang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECopper%20stockpiles%20at%20COMEX-registered%20warehouses%20soared%20170%25%20to%20253%2C431%20short%20tons%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20level%20in%2021%20years%2C%20per%20exchange%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20inventories%20at%20LME%20facilities%20have%20dropped%20roughly%2050%25%20this%20year%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20how%20much%20metal%20was%20diverted%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20now%20an%20excess%20inventory%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20that%20stockpile%20might%20now%20be%20re-exported%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Manthey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20bearish%20for%20LME%20prices%20with%20more%20copper%20now%20showing%20up%20in%20LME%20warehouses%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fwhite-house%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20ruled%20out%20future%20tariffs.%20It%20said%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20recommended%20a%20phased%20universal%20duty%20on%20refined%20copper%3A%2015%25%20in%202027%20and%2030%25%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20ordered%20a%20mark