%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDiana%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20teaching%20her%20how%20to%20build%20a%20meaningful%20life%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Self%20Magazine%20published%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20actor%20spoke%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fself-care%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epracticing%20self-care%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20she%20learned%20to%20be%20comfortable%20on%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20come%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20abundance%2C%20but%20all%20of%20the%20abundance%20that%20I%20enjoy%20is%20mine%2C%20that%20I've%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20told%20Self%20Magazine.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20building%20my%20own%20life%20has%20made%20me%20very%20aware%20of%20what%20my%20mother%20built%20on%20her%20own%20and%20what%20it%20took%20for%20her%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20is%20the%20elder%20of%20two%20children%20from%20Diana%20Ross's%20marriage%20to%20music%20executive%20Robert%20Ellis%20Silberstein.%20She%20also%20has%20an%20older%20half-sister%20from%20her%20mother's%20relationship%20with%20Motown%20founder%20Berry%20Gordy%20and%20two%20younger%20half-brothers%20from%20her%20mother's%20second%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20said%20her%20mother's%20success%20inspired%20her%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BMy%20mom%5D%20didn't%20build%20the%20wealth%20she%20has%2C%20she%20didn't%20build%20the%20career%20she%20made%20because%20of%20a%20man.%20The%20example%20that%20was%20set%20for%20me%20%5Bwas%5D%20that%20I%20didn't%20need%20a%20man%20to%20build%20the%20life%20I%20wanted.%20It%20wasn't%2C%20'Look%20at%20me%2C'%20it%20was%2C%20'This%20is%20me.'%20And%20that%20informed%20something%20very%20important%20for%20me%20foundationally%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20comfortable%20alone%20starts%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20how%20to%20care%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKnowing%20how%20to%