0America%2C%20and%20Asia%20becoming%20kind%20of%20regional%20businesses%20with%20tariff%20rates%20that%20are%20aligned%20for%20those%20three%20or%20four%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20quite%20a%20fundamental%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Ford%20and%20the%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20reduced%20tariffs%20on%20Japan%20would%20give%20its%20Asian%20rivals%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%26quot%3B%20cost%20advantage.%20Last%20week%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20US%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-japan-trade-deal-trump-sp500-tsla-goog-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20its%20tariffs%20on%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2015%25%20from%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reduced%20tariffs%2C%20lower%20labour%20costs%2C%20and%20favorable%20exchange%20rates%20%26quot%3Breally%20advantage%20their%20export%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Kentucky-built%20Ford%20Escape%20could%20cost%20%245%2C000%20more%20than%20a%20Japanese-made%20Toyota%20Rav4%2C%20while%20a%20Michigan-made%20Ford%20Bronco%20might%20be%20undercut%20by%20a%20Toyota%204Runner%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%2410%2C000%2C%20Farley%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20Ford%20is%20working%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20%26quot%3Bminimize%20our%20tariff%20expense%20so%20that%20we%20can%20get%20more%20competitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20bottom%20line%20is%20our%20plan%20at%20Ford%20is%20not%20to%20compete%20in%20those%20commodity%20segments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Farley%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3