r.com%2Fford-trump-tariffs-cost-2-billion-benefit-japanese-rivals-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drones%20were%20just%20used%20to%20drop%20an%20electric%20bike%20on%20the%20battlefield%20for%20a%20stranded%20soldier%2C%20Ukrainian%20brigade%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20photo%20shows%20a%20Heavy%20Shot%20quadcopter%20appearing%20to%20carry%20an%20e-bike%2C%20while%20another%20shows%20the%20camera%20of%20the%20quadcopter%20appearing%20to%20drop%20the%20bike%20to%20the%20soldier.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688aec45f748d8c055f69a64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20brigade's%20team%20said%20it%20took%20three%20tries%20to%20deliver%20the%20bike%20to%20the%20soldier%2C%20who%20was%20trapped%20by%20Russian%20troops.%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRubizh%26quot%3B%204th%20Brigade%20NGU%20YouTube%20Channel%2FScreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Ukrainian%20brigade%20said%20it%20used%20an%20FPV%20drone%20to%20deliver%20an%20escape%20bike%20to%20a%20trapped%20soldier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20chief%20of%20staff%20said%20it%20took%20three%20tries%20with%20a%20Heavy%20Shot%20drone%20to%20make%20a%20successful%20drop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20one%20of%20the%20first%20recorded%20instances%20of%20an%20FPV%20drone%20being%20used%20for%20such%20logistics%20in%20a%20warzone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20brigade%20said%20it%20used%20first-person-view%20drones%20to%20deliver%20e-bikes%20to%20a%20surrounded%20soldier%2C%20marking%20a%20rare%20instance%20where%20such%20devices%20were%20used%20to%20airlift%20a%20vehicle%20in%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20published%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BRubizh%26quot%3B%204th%20Brigade%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fballroom-dancer-ukraine-serhii-naza