%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExpanding%20reach%20across%20districts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20interventions%20were%20predominantly%20focused%20on%20solar%20energy%2C%20primarily%20because%20PM-KUSUM%20served%20as%20the%20overarching%20scheme%20under%20which%20these%20training%20and%20skill%20development%20activities%20took%20place.%20These%20sessions%20initially%20commenced%20in%20the%20Dumka%20district%20and%20were%20subsequently%20extended%20to%20nearly%20all%20eleven%20other%20mining%20districts.%20Members%20of%20FPOs%20in%20each%20district%20participated%20in%20two%20rounds%20of%20training%20at%20their%20respective%20KVK%20centres%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20districts%20involved%20included%20%3Cstrong%3EDumka%2C%20Ramgarh%2C%20Ranchi%2C%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EChatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20with%20later%20sessions%20reaching%20%3Cstrong%3EPalamu%2C%20Chaibasa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EGiridih%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20These%20efforts%20spanned%20from%20%3Cstrong%3E2020%20to%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1753713144.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Awareness%20sessions%20helped%20farmers%20understand%20loans%2C%20credits%2C%20and%20solar-powered%20irrigation%20benefits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1753713144.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1753713144-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1753713144-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1753713