block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20role%20of%20green%20associates%20in%20field-level%20problem%20solving%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporting%20the%20success%20of%20these%20schemes%20are%20the%20Green%20Associates%E2%80%94field%20personnel%20who%20facilitate%20community%20meetings%2C%20coordinate%20inter-departmental%20tasks%2C%20and%20resolve%20beneficiary%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%20for%20the%20Green%20Associate%20role%20under%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20framework%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20candidates%20typically%20need%20a%20postgraduate%20degree%20(preferably%20in%20sustainability%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20or%20environmental%20science)%20and%202%E2%80%933%20years%20of%20field%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20impact%20has%20been%20notable.%20As%20Naman%20Priyesh%20Lakra%2C%20former%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Giridih%2C%20shares%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20facing%20issues%20with%20some%20infrastructure%20with%20previously%20installed%20solar%20systems.%20Following%20the%20process%2C%20we%20corresponded%20with%20various%20departments%20regarding%20its%20repair.%20However%2C%20the%20intervention%20of%20our%20Green%20Associate%20was%20such%20that%20he%20helped%20us%20identify%20the%20exact%20lacunae%20and%20how%20to%20rectify%20them%20through%20the%20nodal%20person.%20And%20to%20our%20pleasant%20surprise%2C%20the%20system%20got%20repaired%20in%20no%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-8_11zon-1753713360.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Green%20Associates%20act%20as%20the%20bridge%20between%20farmers%2C%20local%20governance%2C%20and%20technical%20teams%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20implementation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-8_11zon-17537