20the%20green%20economy%20holds%20promise.%20A%202024%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.climatepolicyinitiative.org%2Fpublication%2Fjust-transition-in-jharkhand-opportunities-for-greening-jobs%2F%5C%22%3EClimate%20Policy%20Initiative%20%3C%2Fa%3Eprojects%20that%20Jharkhand%20could%20generate%20between%2081%2C332%20to%20137%2C172%20direct%20and%20311%2C410%20to%20492%2C924%20indirect%20green%20jobs%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20As%20the%20report%20underscores%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJharkhand%E2%80%99s%20heavy%20reliance%20on%20solid%20fossil%20fuel%20mining%20necessitates%20a%20strategic%20shift%20to%20economic%20diversification%20and%20green%20energy%20for%20a%20sustainable%20future%2C%20thus%20necessitating%20a%20just%20transition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1753713463.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20solar%20irrigation%20to%20assembly%20jobs%2C%20green%20transitions%20aim%20to%20create%20thousands%20of%20sustainable%20livelihoods.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1753713463.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1753713463-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1753713463-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1753713463-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1753713463-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20solar%20irrigation%20to%20assembly%20jobs%2C%20green%20transitions%20aim%20to%20create%20thousands%20of%20sustainable%20livelihoods.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20green%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%20employment%20opportunities%20span%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20sectors%E2%80%94from%20clean%20power%20generation%20to%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20manufacturing%2C%20green%20equipment%20production%2C%20and%20nature-based%20entrepreneurship.%20Recognising%20this%2C%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative%20partnered%20with%20the%20State%20Department%20of%20Employment%20to%20conduct%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20over%2050%20private%20companies%20operating%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20these%20engagements%2C%20one%20clear%20insight%20emerged%3A%20leveraging%20and%20revitalising%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20employment%20exchanges%20at%20the%20district%20level%20is%20essential%20to%20enabling%20growth%20in%20the%20green%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInsights%20from%20the%20private%20sector%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swaniti%20Initiative%E2%80%99s%20conversations%20with%20employers%20revealed%20several%20key%20findings%20on%20how%20to%20unlock%20the%20potential%20of%20green%20job%20creation%20through%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20employment%20ecosystem%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAwareness%20and%20Mobilisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EMany%20companies%20are%20still%20unaware%20of%20the%20existence%20and%20utility%20of%20local%20employment%20exchanges.%20This%20indicates%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20better%20outreach%20and%20information%20dissemination.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutreach%20and%20Communication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEmployment%20exchanges%20must%20proactively%20engage%20with%20employers%20across%20India%2C%20not%20just%20within%20Jharkhand%2C%20to%20broaden%20recruitment%20networks.%20Strategic%20collaborations%E2%80%94with%20local%20organisations%2C%20call%20centres%2C%20and%20CSR-backed%20training%20programs%20can%20generate%20new%20local%20employment%20avenues.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkill%20Training%20and%20Upskilling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EPublic-private%20partnerships%20with%20training%20providers%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20NSDC%20model%2C%20can%20strengthen%20skill%20development%20initiatives.%20The%20Career%20Centre%20should%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Skill%20Development%20Department%20to%20connect%20job%20seekers%20with%20online%20certification%2C%20government%20schemes%2C%20and%20sector-specific%20training.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterdepartmental%20Coordination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEmployment%20exchanges%20can%20act%20as%20intermediaries%20to%20help%20employers%20navigate%20permits%2C%20licenses%2C%20and%20access%20to%20subsidies%20by%20coordinating%20across%20government%20departments%E2%80%94making%20the%20process%20less%20fragmented.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDatabase%20of%20Informal%20Workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEstablishing%20a%20digital%20registry%20of%20informal%20workers%2C%20especially%20in%20sectors%20like%20waste%20management%2C%20is%20essential%20for%20transitioning%20them%20into%20formal%2C%20stable%20employment.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202023%E2%80%9324%2C%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20green%20jobs%20created%20through%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20employment%20exchanges%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative%20and%20other%20agencies%2C%20has%20not%20been%20publicly%20disclosed.%20However%2C%20green%20jobs%20are%20now%20being%20listed%20on%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20official%20employment%20portal%E2%80%94indicating%20that%20institutional%20mechanisms%20are%20being%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20t