ent%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%20and%20educational%20initiatives%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Workshops%20in%20universities%20(for%20example%2C%20at%20SNDT%20Women%E2%80%99s%20University%20in%20January%202023)%20and%20local%20craft%20fairs%20bring%20Pattachitra%20artists%20together%20with%20young%20students%20and%20curious%20audiences%2C%20keeping%20traditional%20knowledge%20alive.%20Grassroots%20groups%20and%20cultural%20enterprises%20such%20as%20Banglanatak%20(UNESCO%2FEU%E2%80%91backed)%20collaborate%20with%20over%203%2C000%20artists%20to%20raise%20awareness%2C%20preserve%20livelihood%2C%20and%20support%20themes%20beyond%20mythology%2C%20ranging%20from%20health%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigital%20and%20exhibition%20platforms%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Artisanal%20platforms%20and%20online%20marketplaces%20permit%20artisans%20to%20reach%20global%20audiences%20directly%E2%80%AF.%20Exhibitions%20both%20within%20India%2C%20including%20Odisha%20Crafts%20Mela%2C%20and%20international%20collaborations%20introduce%20Pattachitra%20to%20new%20collectors%E2%80%AF.%20Digitisation%20and%20virtual%20reality%20(VR)%20experiments%20are%20underway%20to%20preserve%20scrolls%20virtually%2C%20making%20them%20accessible%20worldwide%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternational%20recognition%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20diplomatic%20gesture%20in%20mid%E2%80%912025%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20presented%20a%20Pattachitra%20painting%20from%20Odisha%20to%20the%20president%20of%20Croatia%2C%20generating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387993%2Findira-dhar-putul-journey-cannes-success-filmmaking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20intere